thankful. By the time I’m finished this bitch will be thanking me for every
second of life that I grant her.
“Well?” Saul asks, cutting through the mental image already seeping
into my brain.
“Well, what?” I reply.
“Is she…” He glances to my brother then back at me. “Is she agreeing
to meet?”
“Yes,” I state, before pocketing the phone and turning away. We may
have a few hours, but I want this all executed perfectly. I want her tied up
and gift-wrapped, and more importantly, I want everyone who attends her
